%F A097924 G.f.: (2-x)/(1-4*x-x^2). (End)
%F A097924 G.f.: G(0)*(2-x)/2, where G(k) = 1 + 1/(1 - x*(8*k + 4 +x)/(x*(8*k + 8 +x) + 1/G(k+1) )); (continued fraction). - _Sergei N. Gladkovskii_, Feb 15 2014
